des: The skill currently only supports Degrassi: Next Generation. Degrassi Junior High, Degrassi High, and Next Class are planned to be included in a future release that will let you specify which series you'd like to choose from. Simply "...Ask Degrassi Random Episode what I should watch," to get started!
